gomodel:SYNGO_4070  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immunoreaction product for NPFF is localised on Large dense-core vesicles in Figure 2C (marked by white arrows), Figure 3A (marked by arrowheads) and Figure 4C (marked by arrows).\n\nThe author comments on no cross-reactivity with neuropeptide Y (NPY), peptide YY (PYY), bovine pancreatic polypeptide, Met-enkephalin-Arg-Phe and unrelated peptides such as substance P and bombesin.. Experimental description: Adult male Wistar rats were used for the EM study." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2916-7616" ;
